Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:37.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The mutton here was surprisingly good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:41.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we were celebrating\N and getting drunk last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.77,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so we couldn't exchange much information, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I do recall something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:50.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through our conversation, your wife's story completely captivated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as a drunkard's tale and forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:58.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, even so, your wife is pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:03.17,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and Helpless Partner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:06.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:07.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:11.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have confirmed the presence of the man known as Zeiren.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.95,0:02:14.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We will also continue with our side of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:15.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I was truly surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:21.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought events would play out like this so soon after our meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:24.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The head of the family was quite cautious,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:27.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but when he thought about it, it wasn't that simple of a scam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:31.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to hoard the weakening silver coin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:34.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,someone spread lies that its value would increase,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and persuaded merchants to buy and accumulate coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality, the value is decreasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:44.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so, in a panic, the merchants will attempt to relinquish it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:48.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,At this juncture, the manipulator will swoop in and buy them all in one stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:53.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The merchants who were deceived will keep it a secret, in order to protect their honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:03:00.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There is also a scheme you can use to make a tremendous profit from weakening silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:04.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this undertaking carries a great risk along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:10.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to say that you have piqued my interest once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is a lesson for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like with your marten pelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they'll discover it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if your hypothesis is correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:28.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,if the Milone Company fails to act quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,their efforts to find the conspirator behind Zeiren will be for naught, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I am quite sure that it will turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:40.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for a business to succeed in a foreign land,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:43.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,they should at least have the means to investigate one-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:47.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered something from long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,From looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there was a young man who was doing what you were doing just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and he fell back so wonderfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:06.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned him almost endlessly, but he just never listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you had fun when you were with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:12.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he was quite the dunce, but he was also very cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't a bit surprised when he saw my wolf form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a weird boy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,he was also a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:25.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the first person in my life who treated me like a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:27.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He was from Pasroe village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:30.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the person who asked about the village's wheat field?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He really was a dunce, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I had something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the tip of my tongue, but I simply cannot remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:00.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something fairly important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll remember it soon, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:32.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the branch manager, Marle Height.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:36.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We accept the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:39.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean you've discovered the conspirators behind Zeiren?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:43.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Medioh Company is backing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Medioh Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall, they deal in farming goods with Pattsio and Zuiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're also known for their transportation ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:58.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be impossible for them to execute the plan you hypothesized on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:02.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There is most likely a group of nobles backing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't yet found out exactly whom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but no matter who it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,if we work together and strike first, anything could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:16.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us discuss our shares.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hundred thousand Thoreni silver coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:27.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if all goes well, we can do it with four hundred thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming that the company will make a 10% profit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:33.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,if I get two thousand, I'll finally become a legitimate shop owner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:38.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad that things seem to be going well for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to rest at the inn if you had a hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:47.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried that you would not be able to cajole them correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant exactly what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The inn is right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a drawing of your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting too surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:27.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that great though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on opening up a shop soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That depends on whether the deal with the Milone Company goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm almost certain it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's every peddler's dream to open up their own shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can set up a shop, I'll be a part of the city, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:53.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a peddler, I'll be able to make close friends, and it'll be easier to find a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wonder how Chloe is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be surprised if I open a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she would probably feel bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... a bit troublesome for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to leave once you open a shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:18.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have to continue my travels alone, or find another companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:23.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're clever and you have the money you earned from the marten furs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you'll be fine, traveling on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:37.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't force you to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can accompany you until you return to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can open a shop right away once I obtain the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I always have the same dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:08.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Yueh, nor Intii...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither are Poro or Miyori...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where I look, they're nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:23.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live for several hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we went on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:31.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We thought that we would reunite for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:34.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But... There's no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:39.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to wake up and find that there's no one here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone is cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone is lonely. {har har yeah I know but that's what she says. by the way, DON'T USE VLC FAGGOT}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is shameful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Peddlers have nightmares like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is all sticky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:05.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:08.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to throw away this sketch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, that deal hasn't succeeded yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit to my optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply indebted to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to sleep, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The candle charges will be wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:39.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a very merchant-like notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:01.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything uncouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suffocating...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Have your eyes adjusted yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:27.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally remembered what I had to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three people outside the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:33.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably not your usual guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:35.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... the Medioh Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, there is no one outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:43.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:49.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's thoroughly bathe my body in the moonlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to give up the wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't benefit from killing the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:17.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just get it back once things calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to some, just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:33.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wheat I reside in, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're heading for the Milone Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them make it inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:48.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo, let's go shopping once this matter is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you a comb, a hat, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:57.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, it's just that you have beautiful hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:02.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have a comb for my tail than for my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:04.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll go with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on, we're almost at the Milone Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The gang will be coming soon, let's scour the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation is pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea, but I have a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:27.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:31.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll run out and distract them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.17,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,During that time, you will-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, that's-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:34.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:38.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't split up properly, you'll be the one they capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A wolf like me won't be captured easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,how will I negotiate with the Milone Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You will explain it all to Milone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for you to not be dismissed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to be the one to negotiate for what you want with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go through with this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:02.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Medioh Company sees your ears or tail, they'll take you to the church for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:08.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I am caught, I can hide my ears and tail for at least a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll come rescue me during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:12.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to save up and open a store, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:20.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the perfect chance for me to pay you back for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be killed if you're caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How does that balance out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:29.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness is a fatal disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's balanced enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:45.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:51.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:55.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lawrence! We met earlier today! I'm being chased!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:21.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand him over to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:32.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This establishment is officially recognized by the 33rd Archduke of the Duchy of Laundile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Duke Milone's Milone Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This gate belongs to the Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone within this building is the Duke's guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:45.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, the Duke's guests are under the care and protection of Archduke Laundile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:52.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Hitting this fence with that stick of yours is the same as hitting the Archduke's pedestal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite the uproar in the middle of the night, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And above all, I thank you all for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:14.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to give thanks, go offer it to the distant Duke Milone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:20.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They were most likely receiving orders from the Medioh Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:25.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The business proposal I brought here was exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're trying to obstruct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Obstruct it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:31.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility that my companion was captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you bring her back with your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:40.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of our people who heard the uproar went out to gather information,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:45.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and reported that they saw a female being forcibly taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably my companion, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She decided to be a decoy so that I could make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:59.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, for what reason did they capture her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:06.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to prevent us from interfering with the Medioh Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:12.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:16.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down. Something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They have your companion as a hostage now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but is there anything they can do to obstruct us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have already begun to hoard Thoreni silver coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:36.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is to say, we already know all the details behind the underground dealings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:39.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had simply gathered Thoreni silver coins
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:44.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and had not told anyone about it, then there would be value in taking a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:49.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there aren't any stores that would take action in that situation, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.26,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:56.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we have already gathered all the information we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what happens to you or your companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:04.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very unfortunate, but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:07.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we have already invested a vast amount into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to weigh the potentially outrageous profit we could make,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,with the bitterness that you would have with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:18.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I have to think of the company's profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that your companion is very important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, letting this dull your thinking would be getting your priorities completely backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If my wife was in the same situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably wouldn't be able to stay calm, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:05.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The Medioh Company should obviously know what we would decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Obvious... I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:16.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, they targeted you, knowing that she wouldn't work as a lever in negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:18.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:22.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:26.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The profit lying before us is an incredible amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I would very much like for us fulfill this undertaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:33.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have even the slightest idea, please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lawrence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:39.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an idea, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:50.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter was thrown in earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's connected to this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"To the wolf and the forest it resides in."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but may I read that first?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.50,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"We have the wolf."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"The church doors have already opened."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,"For the wolf to not enter your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.69,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,shut the door together with your family."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My female companion, Horo, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the incarnation of the wolf that brings an abundant harvest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:19.66,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven apples on the witch's tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:25.04,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,With seven seeds to plant inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:30.22,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,In spring time I grew a magic song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:32.96,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Then skipping along,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:35.52,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I sang the song to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.95,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I look at the world through apple eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:46.28,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And cut myself a slice of sunshine pie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:51.62,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I danced with the peanuts for the flies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:54.25,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Till someone had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:57.31,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,To say hello for every good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:23:02.27,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw some sugar stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:07.36,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put them in a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:09.93,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:13.37,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:17.23,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little wolf inside a cart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:18.58,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,You say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:22.87,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,And off I go from June to May
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:28.76,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh we'll wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:32.41,ed_style,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:43.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Lover's Quarrel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:49.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Wolf and Lover's Quarrel
